Visit JWPlayer docs for keyboard shortcuts  Duration:4 minutes, 12 seconds  Green Team participants from Groundwork Anacostia (Washington D.C.) took part in a five day camping trip to Shenandoah National Park. The trip fostered environmental stewardship through service learning and an increased appreciation for the mission of the National Park Service.
